OL,3,CMedical regulator apologises to
OL,4,Cdoctors struck off for their sexuality
OL,6,FAt least eight doctors were struck
OL,7,Foff, and at least 40 subjected to
OL,8,Ffitness-to-practise proceedings, after
OL,9,Fthe General Medical Council (GMC) was
OL,10,Ftold they had engaged in, or tried to
OL,11,Fengage in, consensual sexual activity
OL,12,Fwith other men.
OL,14,FThe GMC said it was issuing a formal
OL,15,Fapology "for taking regulatory action
OL,16,Fagainst doctors who, in historic
OL,17,Fcases, had convictions under now-
OL,18,Frepealed homophobic laws".
