OL,3,CMedical regulator apologises to
OL,4,Cdoctors struck off for their sexuality
OL,6,FThe cases date back to the 1890s, with
OL,7,Fthe last confirmed case of a doctor
OL,8,Fbeing struck off in 1966.
OL,10,FOther doctors have been issued with
OL,11,F'behaviour warnings' over their
OL,12,Fsexuality since then.
OL,14,FChairwoman Professor Dame Carrie
OL,15,FMacEwen said that the homophobic laws
OL,16,Fand attitudes in place caused personal
OL,17,Fand professional harm.
