OL,3,CMedical regulator apologises to
OL,4,Cdoctors struck off for their sexuality
OL,6,F"We compounded that harm when we also
OL,7,Ftook additional regulatory action
OL,8,Fagainst those who were on the medical
OL,9,Fregister," she said.
OL,11,F"In some cases that meant the end of a
OL,12,Fpractitioner's career. For this we are
OL,13,Ftruly sorry."
OL,15,FThe GMC said it does not know exactly
OL,16,Fhow many medical doctors faced
OL,17,Fregulatory action.
